# ============================================================
# HFWastelandZ — Blacklist Configuration
# File: $profile:HFWastelandZ_blacklist.conf
# ============================================================
#
# Local file-based player bans. Players on this list are
# kicked immediately on spawn. Works alongside the database
# blacklist system for instant enforcement.
#
# FORMAT:
#   BAN <Steam64ID>     — one banned player per line
#
# BEHAVIOR:
#   No config file      → no local bans (DB bans still checked)
#   Empty config        → no local bans
#   BAN entries         → listed players kicked on connect
#
# For database-managed bans (with expiration, scope, etc.)
# use the MotaBot !ban command or gateway API.
#
# ============================================================

# --- BANNED PLAYERS ---
# Add one BAN line per banned player
# Example:
#   BAN 76561198012345678

# BAN 76561198012345678
